---
layout: base.njk
title: "TalkSoon Blog - Speech Language Pathology Resources and Insights"
description: "Expert insights and resources on childhood speech and language development from licensed speech language pathologist Markie. Covering late talkers, autism, stuttering, and more in Southern Zone Costa Rica."
---

<!-- Decorative Frame for Page Header -->
<div class="page-decorative-frame" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true">
    <img src="/images/decor-left.svg" alt="" class="page-decor" role="presentation">
</div>

<div class="page-container">
    <header>
        <h1>TalkSoon Blog</h1>
        <p>Expert insights and practical guidance on childhood speech and language development, covering everything from late talkers to autism support.</p>
    </header>
    
    {% if collections.posts %}
    <section class="blog-posts" aria-labelledby="blog-posts-heading">
        <h2 id="blog-posts-heading" class="visually-hidden">Latest Articles</h2>
        {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <article class="blog-post-preview">
            <header>
                <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
                <div class="post-meta">
                    <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | dateFormat }}</time>
                    {% if post.data.tags %}
                    <div class="post-tags" role="list" aria-label="Article topics">
                        {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                            {% if tag != "posts" %}
                            <span class="tag" role="listitem">#{{ tag }}</span>
                            {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </header>
            {% if post.data.excerpt %}
            <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
            {% endif %}
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more" aria-label="Read full article: {{ post.data.title }}">Read More â†’</a>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
    </section>
    {% else %}
    <section class="no-posts">
        <h2>Coming Soon</h2>
        <p>We're working on bringing you valuable content about speech and language development. In the meantime, explore our services:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/services/late-talker">Late Talker Support</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/difficult-to-understand">Speech Clarity Therapy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Schedule a consultation</a></li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    {% endif %}
</div> 
